<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
    <head>
        <title>Home</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/base.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/media.css">
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <meta name="author" content="Jeremiah Franco">
        <meta name="description" content="Scholar Manager is a web application that 
        helps you keep track of your tuition sessions.">
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <h1><a href="/index">SM</a></h1>
            <nav>
                <div class="hamburger" onclick="toggleMenu()">&#9776;</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <a href="/index">Home</a>
                        <a href="/about">About</a>
                        <a href="/finances">Finances</a>
                        <% if (!loggedIn) { %> <!-- Show Login and Sign Up if not logged in -->
                            <a href="/login">Login</a>
                            <a id="signup" href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
                        <% } else { %> <!-- Show Logout button if logged in -->
                            <form id="logout" action="/logout" method="POST">
                                <button type="submit">Logout</button>
                            </form>
                        <% } %>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <main>
            <section id="who">
                <img src="/spori.jpg" alt="Spori">
                <section id="we">
                    <h1>Who are we?</h1>
                    <p>At Scholar Manager, we understand the unique financial 
                    challenges that college students face. Balancing tuition 
                    payments, living expenses, and student loans can be overwhelming. 
                    That’s why we created this platform—to empower you on your 
                    financial journey</p>
                </section>
            </section>
            <section id="mission">
                <section id="miss">
                    <h1>Our Mission</h1>
                    <p>Our mission is simple: to help college students take control 
                    of their finances. Whether you’re a freshman navigating your
                    first semester or a senior about to graduate, we’ve got your back. 
                    We believe that financial literacy is a crucial life skill, and 
                    we’re here to provide the tools and resources you need.</p>
                </section>
                <img src="/taylor.jpg" alt="Taylor">
            </section>
            <section id="give">
                <h1>What we offer</h1>
                <section id="offer">
                    <section>
                        <h2>Tuition Tracking</h2>
                        <p>
                            Track your tuition payments effortlessly. Input your tuition 
                            amounts, due dates, and payment methods. Our intuitive 
                            dashboard keeps everything organized, so you never miss a deadline.
                        </p>
                    </section>
                    <section>
                        <h2>Expense Management</h2>
                        <p>
                            College life comes with expenses—books, meals, transportation, 
                            and more. Use our expense tracker to log your spending. Set budgets, 
                            receive alerts, and stay on top of your financial game.
                        </p>
                    </section>
                    <section>
                        <h2>Student Loans Made Simple</h2>
                        <p>
                            Got student loans? We’ve got you covered. Input your loan details—interest 
                            rates, repayment terms, and grace periods. Our loan calculator helps you 
                            understand the impact of different repayment strategies.
                        </p>
                    </section>
                </section>
                <div id="slide-indicators">
                    <span class="dot"></span>
                    <span class="dot"></span>
                    <span class="dot"></span>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2021 Personal Tuition Track</p>
            <p>Jeremiah Franco</p>
        </footer>
        <script src="/dots.js"></script>
        <script src="/menu.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>